        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2021-08-06 16:08:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI see the module_name and revision getting stored in yang_resources when a single schema set file is uploaded. Eg : cps-cavsta-onap-internal2021-01-28.yang\nBut when a zip file is saved with multiple files, it doesnt save the module_name and revision in the yang-resources table.\n\nAs this story is related to fetching/listing the modules, the code changes for storing the module_name and revision could be taken as a different task.",
        "patchset_number": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "f3c2beae12585dc222a018d8ae658520a825de08",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 7486,
